{"tid":1838493,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"唔好懶!! 對抗中國肺炎疫情係需要大家自己做起，我地想分享下，希望一齊留意下!","createTime":"2020-01-24T04:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T17:09:21.000Z","uid":1806,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"915fb49fa4348a4c5e3382d6cfc537227e13faff","tid":1838493,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"大家好，又係我地香城教育電視。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n鑒於中國肺炎疫情不斷惡化，因此我地整合一些對抗疫情既小貼士。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">首先由源頭做起，唔好返中國!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n可能各位手足唔會返中國，但日防夜防，家賊難防。難保手足家中既長輩係新年自動送中，然後中埋中國肺炎再返香港。所以各位手足要將關於中國肺炎既疫情係咁家中宣揚，等佢地驚到咁敢送中。我地都會盡力將最新既疫情既資訊係我地TG channel 發放。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第二步，就係日常出外防疫</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n都係靠戴口罩，再提一提大家，普通外科口罩都有一定保護能力。<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">詳細可以睇我地之前關於口罩既post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1813942/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1813942/page/1</a></span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第三步，個人衛生</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住!記住!記住，洗手!洗手!洗手!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n點洗手可以參考衛生防護中心既建議:<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>1. 用水弄濕雙手<br />\n2. 加入梘液，揉搓雙手最少20秒 (手掌 &gt; 手背 &gt; 指隙 &gt; 指背 &gt; 拇指 &gt; 指尖 &gt; 手腕) 勿忘<br />\n3. 用水沖洗乾淨<br />\n4. 用抹手紙抹乾雙手<br />\n5. 再用抹手紙關上水龍頭 </blockquote><br />\n<br />\n港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良並強調用梘液洗手可減少99%至99.9%細菌，相比用水洗手所減的90%為多。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><blockquote>消委會之前已經測試過市面上部份既消毒搓手液，大家可以參巧下。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/article/466-4172?fbclid=IwAR0n0GJb_exMTBOpnPye3O9Iqi5dbpSdwRSRWWsc6t7xrWPUha9amfIfyCU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fechoice.consumer.org.hk%2Farticle%2F466-4172%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0n0GJb_exMTBOpnPye3O9Iqi5dbpSdwRSRWWsc6t7xrWPUha9amfIfyCU&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=b0ed20ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://echoice.consumer.org.hk/article/466-4172?fbclid=IwAR0n0GJb_exMTBOpnPye3O9Iqi5dbpSdwRSRWWsc6t7xrWPUha9amfIfyCU</a></blockquote></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">第四步，家居衛生</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後係日常家居清潔既時候可以考慮用漂白水，滴露等等可以用作消毒既清潔劑。<br />\n以下係幾時要用1:49同1:99既情況:<br />\n<br />\n<strong><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">1:99稀釋家用漂白水（以10毫升漂白水混和於1公升清水內），可用於一般家居清潔。<br />\n1:49稀釋家用漂白水（以10毫升漂白水混和於0.5公升清水內），用於消毒染有嘔吐物、排泄物、分泌物或血液的表面或物件。</span></blockquote></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">另外有一個地方好多從人都無留意就係要蓋廁板沖廁!!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n負責研究的港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良指出，廁板及冲廁掣有較多來自糞便和尿液的細菌或病毒，包括金黃葡萄球菌、沙門氏菌及諾如病毒等常見致病病毒。若廁所曾有病人用過，其他使用者或有機會「中招」染病。<br />\n他又指出，曾<strong><ins>有研究指沖廁時濺出的水花可噴至6呎遠，因此沖廁前應該蓋上廁板；否則若廁所通風差，細菌便會存在空氣中，更易「中招」。至於向尿兜或馬桶吐痰後，應蓋上廁板才沖廁，否則痰中細菌也會隨廁所水飛濺出來</ins></strong>；若有人吐痰吐「出界」，更可能會殃及其他使用者。<br />\n咁大家要點預止呢？<br />\n廁格四周恐被坐廁內隨水花濺出的細菌污染，其中廁紙易受污染。市民應自備紙巾、濕紙巾及酒精搓手液，並先用紙巾和酒精搓手液清潔廁板方可使用坐廁。此外，市民每次如廁後應蓋上廁板才沖廁，然後徹底洗手。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以參考下呢兩篇報道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2531479/【港大研究】每5人只有1人蓋廁板沖廁%E3%80%80專家：細菌黏附皮膚增病毒感染風險\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2531479%2F%E3%80%90%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E3%80%91%E6%AF%8F5%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%AA%E6%9C%891%E4%BA%BA%E8%93%8B%E5%BB%81%E6%9D%BF%E6%B2%96%E5%BB%81%25E3%2580%2580%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%EF%BC%9A%E7%B4%B0%E8%8F%8C%E9%BB%8F%E9%99%84%E7%9A%AE%E8%86%9A%E5%A2%9E%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92%E6%84%9F%E6%9F%93%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=adc16780\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2531479/【港大研究】每5人只有1人蓋廁板沖廁%E3%80%80專家：細菌黏附皮膚增病毒感染風險</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2532002/【公廁危機】4成人沖廁不蓋廁板恐惹菌%20水花可飛濺6呎污染廁紙\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fskypost.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2532002%2F%E3%80%90%E5%85%AC%E5%BB%81%E5%8D%B1%E6%A9%9F%E3%80%914%E6%88%90%E4%BA%BA%E6%B2%96%E5%BB%81%E4%B8%8D%E8%93%8B%E5%BB%81%E6%9D%BF%E6%81%90%E6%83%B9%E8%8F%8C%2520%E6%B0%B4%E8%8A%B1%E5%8F%AF%E9%A3%9B%E6%BF%BA6%E5%91%8E%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E5%BB%81%E7%B4%99&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=f4a988b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://skypost.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2532002/【公廁危機】4成人沖廁不蓋廁板恐惹菌%20水花可飛濺6呎污染廁紙</a><br />\n</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: small;\">HKGETV Social Media Platform<br />\n<strong><blockquote>YouTube Channel: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w%2Ffeatured&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=a1351ee1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCtzu8W55-S9biNCKgHg1v7w/featured</a><br />\nOur Facebook Page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKGETV%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=7dfa2152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKGETV/</a><br />\nOur Instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/HKGETV/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2FHKGETV%2F&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=72af6875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/HKGETV/</a><br />\nOur Twitter: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkgetv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkgetv&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=5c4ebd1c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkgetv</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Telegram Channel (New!):</span><a href=\"https://t.me/hkgetv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkgetv&d=J5HXnbFloTEqGlUzWM3JX52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=4ec32723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkgetv</a></blockquote></strong></span></strong>"},{"pid":"92961ba411968d2ee17e802259b9b8b4546ae8ee","tid":1838493,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845d88aae9e67e420f8f076e8e13015a8ea90721","tid":1838493,"uid":162008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:51:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"3446a28f63fd16c5caddcb740bb5738ec0ac72df","tid":1838493,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"cd214491ed8a3277b03b166ed2be3fff8140a433","tid":1838493,"uid":1806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:53:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"642cbe92f99194fd640d386ef4c92a39dd392163","tid":1838493,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd77e68875e5927a6c03cbf70bbc60b8214a488a","tid":1838493,"uid":113373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:54:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">立即封關 否則罷工</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"250d86d8a90b8caeac4ba8f10369cece401afeec","tid":1838493,"uid":140000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:55:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab6192f944cb7d73c649d2c8448299a2d1a7a5c","tid":1838493,"uid":135554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:57:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f777abbae344f5fd632cf297d30d8061699313d2","tid":1838493,"uid":265316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T04:58:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c5c252421dfe8cca1cc8d17a043c4c6fe5a38a0f","tid":1838493,"uid":2870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:00:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b02f751c2ae0d3b65e73b46c8ead65f7ab4fd33","tid":1838493,"uid":62889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:02:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74b4f13d7381e9581180fe2daff9da380a4c3f4b","tid":1838493,"uid":318634,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:02:33.000Z","msg":"呢個政府唔會幫到我哋啲乜, 入境同埋醫護已經提曬水, 醫護更加有人冧低咗<br />\n<br />\n目標: 驅趕大陸遊客、切斷來港途徑。<br />\n<br />\n地點： 由旺角油麻地一帶推進至香港西九高鐵站不需強攻 震懾效果成功即可 只要影響高鐵運作成功<br />\n<br />\n時間：今日黃昏<br />\n<br />\n嚟嘅麻煩